<bibRefCitation author="Burckhardt" pageId="8" refString="Burckhardt, D. &amp; Basset, Y. (2000) The jumping plant-lice (Hemiptera: Psylloidea) associated with Schinus (Anacardiaceae): systematics, biogeography and host plant relationships. Journal of Natural History, 34, 57 - 155. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 002229300299688" type="journal article" year="2000">Burckhardt &amp; Basset 2000</bibRefCitation>
).— 
<collectingCountry box="[250,366,1704,1729]" name="Colombia" pageId="8">Colombia</collectingCountry>
: 
<taxonomicName authority="(Pinzon &amp; Gonzalez 2002)" authorityName="Pinzon &amp; Gonzalez" authorityYear="2002" baseAuthorityName="Pinzon &amp; Gonzalez" baseAuthorityYear="2002" box="[376,870,1704,1729]" class="Insecta" family="Calophyidae" genus="Calophya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schini">
<emphasis box="[376,559,1704,1729]" italics="true" pageId="8">Calophya schini</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Pinzon" box="[574,863,1704,1729]" pageId="8" refString="Pinzon, O. P. &amp; Gonzalez, R. H. (2002) Caracterizacion biologica, habitos, enemigos naturales y fluctuacion poblacional de Calophya schini Tuthill, en la especie forestal ornamental Schinus molle L. en Bogota. Revista Cientifica, 2002, 137 - 154." type="journal article" year="2002">Pinzón &amp; González 2002</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
